359
00:20:49,082 --> 00:20:51,412
- Hej, Han Gyeol-e. 
- Han Gyeol-e.

360
00:20:52,182 --> 00:20:53,212
Chan Young-u.

361
00:20:53,752 --> 00:20:55,452
Neber si moc to, co řekl.

362
00:20:55,512 --> 00:20:57,682
